title: Zeppelin's War - Night Raiders (2014) (Vargas) cbr
description:
1916: German dirigibles attack Paris!

At the end of 1916, Germany has occupied a good part of Northern France and Paris is bombarded by fleets of Zeppelins.
Among the pilots is a certain Adolf Hitler and the protecting squadron of his Zeppelin is commanded by Hermann Goering.
But Hitler and Goering do not know that their destiny is being decided in the decay of the Russian Empire where a certain Rasputin is about to change the history of Europe.

enjoy
